Class.ClassComment:
TriConsumer /** * Represents an operation that accepts three input arguments and returns no result. This is the three-arity specialization of {@link Consumer}. Unlike most other functional interfaces, {@code TriConsumer} is expectedto operate via side-effects.

This is a functional interface whose functional method is {@link #accept(Object,Object,Object)}. * @param < T > the type of the first argument to the operation * @param < U > the type of the second argument to the operation * @param < V > the type of the third argument to the operation * @author wburns * @since 8.2 */

Method.MethodComment: /** * Performs this operation on the given arguments. * @param t the first input argument * @param u the second input argument * @param v the third input argument */
